Dark One fired off a pair of heat-seeking missiles at Windlord, adding more 
power to his engines, gaining velocity rapidly, closing in on Windlord.

Sixshot sped up his own velocity, firing off another pair of energy-signature 
seeking missiles at Windlord, gaining velocity at a great rate.
